$N, as well as zonal banding within the\nnorth polar region. The difference in brightness is a factor of $\\sim$10 less\npronounced in these bands than the difference between the north pole and\nequator, and additional observations are required to determine the temperature,\ncomposition and vertical extent of these features.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 21 Oct 2020 17:19:13 GMT"}],"update_date":"2020-10-22"}
