ow resolution images, unreliable\nodometry, or lighting change, while requiring significantly less compute. We\nalso - for the first time - demonstrate versatile cross-platform teach and\nrepeat without changing parameters, in which we learn to navigate a route with\none robot and repeat that route using a completely different robot.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 21 Oct 2020 21:53:32 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Mon, 8 Mar 2021 21:16:30 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Thu, 29 Jul 2021 00:07:09 GMT"}],"update_date":"2021-07-30"}
